These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
Color: purple, red, ebony, coral
Transport: taxi, subway, jet-ski, trike
Job: analyst, writer, videographer, accountant
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, palace, wooden
 1. Transport:taxi is on the right of Transport:subway##1
 2. Color:purple is in an even position##4
 3. Job:analyst is on the left of Transport:jet-ski##1
 4. Job:videographer is on the right of Color:coral##1
 5. Transport:taxi is on the left or right of Transport:subway##3
 6. House:craftsman is on the left of Color:red##1
 7. Job:writer == Color:ebony##1
 8. House:palace is in an even position##4
 9. House:craftsman is between House:wooden and Transport:trike##2
10. Color:purple == House:wooden##1
11. Transport:jet-ski == Color:coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Color          | ebony  | purple    | coral    | red   |
| Transport   | subway     | taxi   | jet-ski       | trike    |
| Job   | writer | analyst | accountant    | videographer |
| House           | gothic-revival | wooden       | craftsman | palace     |

