 1. Movie-Genre:crime is in an even position##4
 2. House:art-deco is on the left of City:hamburg##1
 3. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the right of Transport:tram##1
 4. Transport:jet-ski == House:colonial##1
 5. City:hannover is on the right of Transport:subway##1
 6. House:colonial is on the left or right of House:craftsman##3
 7. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Transport:tram##1
 8. House:cape-cod is on the left or right of City:new-york##3
 9. House:craftsman is on the far left or far right##3
10. Transport:tram is in an odd position##4
11. House:craftsman == Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport          | subway  | jet-ski    | tram     | quad-bike       |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie | crime | action   | mystery |
| House   | craftsman | colonial   | art-deco   | cape-cod    |
| City         | prague | hannover  | new-york | hamburg   |

